---
import Layout from "../components/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Features - Turbin Engines">
    <div class="bg-blue-900 text-white py-16 px-6">
        <div class="container mx-auto text-center">
            <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold leading-tight mb-4">Turbin Engine Features</h1>
            <p class="text-lg mb-8">Explore the advanced features that make Turban aircraft engines exceptional in the aviation industry.</p>
            <a href="#" class="bg-white text-blue-900 py-2 px-6 rounded-full hover:bg-gray-200 transition">Learn More</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Feature 1 -->
    <div class="bg-gray-100 py-16 px-6">
        <div class="container mx-auto">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">Efficiency Redefined</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-10">Turbin engines are designed for maximum efficiency, providing optimal performance while minimizing fuel consumption. The innovative design and advanced technology contribute to enhanced fuel efficiency, making Turban engines a cost-effective solution for aircraft owners.</p>
                <img src="../../public/images/engine1.jpeg" alt="Efficiency Image" class="w-full max-w-3xl rounded-lg shadow-md">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Feature 2 -->
    <div class="bg-white py-16 px-6">
        <div class="container mx-auto">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">Advanced Technology Integration</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-10">Turbin engines incorporate state-of-the-art technology to deliver reliability, durability, and unmatched performance in aviation. The integration of advanced systems and sensors ensures precise control, efficient power delivery, and a smooth flight experience for pilots and passengers alike.</p>
                <img src="../../public/images/engine2.jpeg" alt="Technology Image" class="w-full max-w-3xl rounded-lg shadow-md">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Feature 3 -->
    <div class="bg-gray-100 py-16 px-6">
        <div class="container mx-auto">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">Sleek and Modern Design</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-10">The Turbin engines not only excel in performance but also feature a modern and sleek design. The aerodynamic design enhances the overall efficiency and performance of the aircraft. Turbin engines not only power your flight but also add a touch of elegance to your aircraft's appearance.</p>
                <img src="../../public/images/engine3.jpeg" alt="Design Image" class="w-full max-w-3xl rounded-lg shadow-md">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
